# Node.js 

To install create-react-app globally
$ npm i -g create-react-app

To create project folder
create-react-app

after installing check the installation


To create project folder
$ npx create-react-app weather_app

change directory to root folder:

$ cd weather-app

To install packages
$ npm install

To start the dev server
$ npm start

