components 2 types

	functional and class based

function funName() {}

Arrow funtion: 

    () => {}

    var myArrowFunc = () => {}


class based component:

class Test extends React.Component{
	render() {
	   return (
             <div>TEst</div>
           )
        }
}

export default Test;



first line is mandatory for every file:
import React from 'react'


importing/exporting two types:
	1.defaut
	2.named

	default export:
		export default ComponentName;
        named export:
		export ComponentName;


	default import:
		import ComponentName from 'file path';
	named import:
		import { ComponentName } from 'file path';


